text: Pajarito may refer to: ==Places== * Pajarito, Boyacá, a town and municipality in the La Libertad Province, Boyacá, Columbia * Pajarito Plateau, a volcanic plateau in north central New Mexico, United States * Pajarito Formation, a Mesozoic geologic formation in the New Mexico and Texas, United States ==People== * Roberto "Pajarito" Buitrago (born 1937), Colombian road racing cyclist * Nicasio Pajarito Gonzalez (born 1935), Mexican potter known for his canelo ware ==See also== * Pajarito Mountains (disambiguation) * Pajaritos (disambiguation)
title: Pajarito
